Pacific Senior International Results
February 16, 2008

      Saskatchewan was represented by 12 athletes at the Pacific Senior Internationals in Steveston, B.C.

      Here are the individual results:

        • Kendal McArthur, 1 win, 2 losses
        • Emin Sheykhislyamov, 4 wins, 2 losses
        • Jordan Poliakiwski, 1 win, 3 losses
        • Ian MacDonald, 1 win, 2 losses
        • Nichelle Stever, 1 win, 2 losses
        • Ashley McBride, 1 win, 3 losses
        • Ryan Potts, 2 wins, 2 losses
        • Michela Carriere, 2 losses
        • Shane Kivol, 4 wins, 1 loss, SILVER medal
        • Jim Wiens, 1 win, 2 losses
        • Dilyaver Sheykhislyamov, 4 wins, 2 losses
        • Chris Tinga, 2 losses
